        {
            "title": "華潤萬象生活去年純利升10.3% 派末期加特別息每股合共0.85元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華潤萬象生活(01209)公布，於2025年度錄得股東應佔淨利潤39.7億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升10.3%；擬派末期加特別息每股合共0.85元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入已派中期息每股0.529元，該公司全年每股合共派息1.379元，仍較2024年度每股派息合共2.111元減少逾34%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">去年該公司收入180.2億元，按年升5.1%。毛利64.1億元，增長13.3%；毛利率35.5%，按年提升2.5個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若按非香港財務報告準則計量，期內股東應佔核心淨利潤39.5億元，按年升13.7%。有效淨現金流達44.37億元，有效淨現金流對核心淨利潤的覆蓋倍數為1.1倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810225-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e8%90%ac%e8%b1%a1%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%8710-3-%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e5%8a%a0%e7%89%b9%e5%88%a5%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a1%e5%90%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01209.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 08:23:12",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期低水逾400點 建行ADR績後逆市反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時11分跌409點或1.64%，報24536點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報24705點，較香港上日現貨收市低246點或0.99%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣487.1元，較上日香港收市低6.34元或1.29%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣120.1元，較上日香港收市低2.47元或2.02%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣84.6元，較上日香港收市低1.26元或1.47%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣112.4元，較上日香港收市低1.3元或1.14%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣32.6元，較上日香港收市低0.37元或1.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣124.1元，較上日香港收市低0.74元或0.59%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣85元，較上日香港收市低0.6元或0.7%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣384.1元，較上日香港收市低6.35元或1.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣58.4元，較上日香港收市低0.9元或1.53%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.2元，較上日香港收市高0.08元或0.99%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/bplib_20230712-141204_00939_shutterstock_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/bplib_20230712-141204_00939_shutterstock_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報24630點，跌221點，較上日恒指收市24951點，低水322點。科指期貨夜市收報4683點，較上日科指收市低水95點；國指期貨夜市收報8340點，較上日國指收市低水114點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810241-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e-%e5%bb%ba%e8%a1%8cadr%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 08:18:14",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "遇見小麵盈利升逾70%  末期0.03元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">遇見小麵(02408)截至2025年12月31日非國際準則計量經調整淨利潤1.35億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升111.9%，股東應佔利潤1.04億元，按年升70.6%，末期息0.03元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：遇見小麵官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_XN-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遇見小麵官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_XN-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：遇見小麵官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入16.22億元，按年升40.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">餐廳數量由2024年的306間增至503間，同店銷售額增幅1%，2023年至2024年則減4.2%，同店單店日均訂單432宗，按年增9.92%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15801603-%e9%81%87%e8%a6%8b%e5%b0%8f%e9%ba%b5%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be70-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f0-03%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250415_FI_source-web_Xiao-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 18:31:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新世界百貨委任胡玉君為行政總裁",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新世界百貨(00825)公布，委任胡玉君為執行董事兼公司行政總裁，自2026年4月1日起生效。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">胡玉君60歲，1993年加入新世界百貨，於2003年晉升為企業事務總監，直至2014年調任為K11 Concepts Limited(“K11”)的營運董事，隨後於2018年7月晉升為K11的資深營運董事。於2025年3月離開K11以投放更多時間在個人發展上。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15801525-%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e7%99%be%e8%b2%a8%e5%a7%94%e4%bb%bb%e8%83%a1%e7%8e%89%e5%90%9b%e7%82%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%94%bf%e7%b8%bd%e8%a3%81",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_00825-704-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 18:21:23",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "迅策股東應佔虧損逾9400萬人幣  收入增逾倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「詞元Token第一股」迅策(03317)公布截至2025年12月31日業績，母公司擁有人應佔虧損9406.1萬元(人民幣‧下同)，2024同期為8401.1萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"迅策官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"迅策官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">迅策官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">經調整虧損5485萬元，2024年為8236.6萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入12.85億元，按年升103.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，收入大幅增長主要由於AI大模型落地所帶動的數據需求激<br/>   增。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司表示，隨著openclaw等出現，集團正深度參與AI操作系統生<br/>   態建設，構建「數據token化」服務，致力成為新操作系統中不可或缺的核心數據token供應商。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">迅策(03317)午後飆升，成交入20大，收升24.25%，報188.5元，最高見197元，為上市新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15801450-%e8%bf%85%e7%ad%96%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%87%89%e4%bd%94%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e9%80%be9400%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e5%a2%9e%e9%80%be%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 18:09:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "建行歸屬股東淨利升1.53%  末期息減1.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">建設銀行(00939)公布，截至2025年12月31日歸屬於普通股股東的淨利潤3334.86億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升1.53%，淨利潤3397.79億元，按年升1.04%。每股收益1.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">末期息每10股2.029元，較2024年度末期息每10股2.060元降1.5%，計及中期息1.858元，全年派息3.887元，較2024年全年派息4.03元減3.55%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source_licensed_00939_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source_licensed_00939_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">經營收入7408.71億元，按年升1.69%，其中利息淨收入按年減2.9%，至5727.74億元，手續費及佣金淨收入1103.07億元，按年升5.13%，其他非利息淨收入577.9億元，按年升71.18%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">信用減值損失1333.17億元，按年增加10.45% ; 其他資產減值損失4200萬元，按年減85.91%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不良貸款率1.31%，較2024年度1.34%下降，不良貸款金額3639.82億元，較2024年3446.91億元高5.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15801423-%e5%bb%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%ad%b8%e5%b1%ac%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%871-53-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%b8%9b1-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230719_FI_source_licensed_00939_CCB_shutterstock_704.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-27 17:51:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
